revision.text:
'''Suwa Yorimitsu''' ([[1480]]-[[1540]]) Suwa Yorimitsu, a warlord of the [[Shinano Province]]. In the province of Shinano, the region that was controlled by Yorimitsu was [[Lake Suwa]]. During the year of [[1485]], Yorimitsu's father was killed by his own retainers for unknown reasons. But Yorimitsu in the end was a very capable leader, greatly strengthening the domain of [[Suwa]].
{{Japan-bio-stub}}
